metadata.name: The Forgotten Soul, Trapped Away for an Eternity
metadata.description:
Sitting in the manifestations of reality and distorted self-experience.

"The Forgotten Soul, Trapped away for an Eternity" is an expression of the loss of control of one's individuality and being. As the Soul desperately tries to escape its binds, to be unchained from Oblivion.

We struggle in what's thought to be our "Wasted Form" believing that we are the problem and the world would be better without us. As we stand looking into the Edge of the Abyss. 

Corrupted and Altered into an empty shell, a chrysalis of the Mortal Coil.

Seeking this new carapace, to grow and develop into something anew.

We must seek "Our Escape."

The Best thing we can do is to reach out and talk about our issues and disorder, for they do not make us who we are. We drive our own path forward.

Artworks are created only using “Artificial Intelligence/ Machine Learning software”

50% of ETH will be Donated to Mental Health Association/Charities
